  "keyFeatures": [
    "Decentralized news aggregation from Sui ecosystem sources",
    "Article tipping with SUI tokens on Sui blockchain",
    "Commenting system with on-chain and Walrus storage",
    "Hybrid storage: short content on-chain, long content on Walrus",
    "React hooks for news fetching and blockchain interactions",
    "Sui wallet integration with @mysten/dapp-kit",
    "Modern React 19 UI with TypeScript and Vite"
